@node "Distribution" "Distribution "

                       @{b}@{u}Distribution@{ub}@{uu}


GMsuite is freely distributable, but remains (c) Gian Maria Calzolari, 1999.

It may not be included in any commercial distribution without prior consent.
Such consent is already given to include it on the Aminet CDs.

It may be included on magazine cover disks or CDs, provided notification is
sent beforehand. A copy of the magazine and disk would be most welcome.

Of course the single scripts cannot be distribuited, only the complete
package can be!

Please sent bug reports, suggestions and eventually cash :-) to me at
mailto:@{b}gcalzo@geocities.com@{ub}

Even a simple "hey, I'm using this wonderfull scripts" is welcome! :-)

If you like traveling you may want to have a look at mine web pages about
MotorCycle Travels! http://www.geocities.com/TheTropics/Paradise/6362/


Note: my snail-mail address will be eventually given by private mail... :-)
@endnode

